Why don&#39;t you try **Enabling Multidex support** in your app.  
  
In ```project/app/build.gradle``` add  
```gradle
defaultConfig{
  ...
  multidexEnabled true
}
```  
and  
```gradle
dependencies{
  ...
  implementation &#39;com.android.support:multidex:1.0.3&#39;
}
```  
If you migrate to androidX use  
```gradle
dependencies{
  ...
  implementation &#39;androidx.multidex:multidex:2.0.1&#39;
}
```  
Hope it helps.

